           incremented on receiving NEW event for attributes on a port."
      ::= { fsMrpPortStatsEntry 5}

fsMrpPortStatsRxJoinInMsgCount OBJECT-TYPE
      SYNTAX      Counter64
      MAX-ACCESS  read-only
      STATUS      current
      DESCRIPTION
