		   is incremented on receiving JOININ event for attributes on a port."
      ::= { fsMrpPortStatsEntry  6}

fsMrpPortStatsRxJoinMtMsgCount OBJECT-TYPE
      SYNTAX      Counter64
      MAX-ACCESS  read-only
